quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  30,33,"w'idha 'asab alnas shdt wbla' deau rabahum mukhlisin lah 'an yakshif eanhum aldr, fa'iidha rhmhm wakashf eanhum drhm 'iidha fariq minhum yaeudun 'iilaa alshirk maratan akhra, fyebdwn mae allah ghyrh"
  30,34,"lykfru bima ataynahum wmnnna bih ealayhim min kashf aldr, wzwal alshdt enhm, fatamataeuu -ayha almshrkwn- balrkha' walssaeat fi hadhih aldnya, fasawf taelamun ma talaqawnah min aleadhab waleqab"
  30,35,"am 'anzalna ealaa hwla' almushrikin brhanana sateana wktabana qateana, yantiq bisihat shrkhm wakufrihim biallah wayath"
  30,36,"w'idha 'adhaqna alnaas minaa niematan min sihat weafyt wrkha', farihuu bdhlk farih btr w'asharin, la farih shkr, wa'iin ysbhm marad wfqr wkhwf wdyq bsbb dhunubihim wmeasyhm, 'iidha hum yayyaswn min zawal dhlk, whdha tabieat 'akthar alnaas fi alrkha' walshdt"
  30,37,"'awalam yaelamuu 'ana allah ywse alrizq liman yasha' amthanana, hal yashkur 'aw ykfr? wydyiqh ealaa man yasha' akhtbarana, hal ysbr 'aw yjze? 'iina fi dhalik altwsye waltadyiq layat liqawm yuminun biallah wyerfwn hikmat allah wrhmth"
  30,38,"faet -ayha almwmn- qrybk haqah min alsilat walsdqt wsayr 'aemal albr, waet alfaqir walmhtaj aldhy ainqatae bih alsabil min alzakat walsdqt, dhlk al'ieta' khayr liladhin yuridun bemlhm wajah allh, waladhin yaemalun hadhih al'aemal wghyrha min 'aemal alkhyr, 'uwlayik hum alfayizun bthwab allah alnnajun min eqabh"
  30,39,"wma aetytm qrdana min almal biqasd alrba, watalab ziadat dhlk alqrd; lyzyd wynmw fi 'amwal alnas, fala yazid eind allh, bal ymhqh wybtlh. wama aetytm min zakat wsdqt llmsthqyn abtigha' mrdat allah wtlbana lthwabh, fhdha hu aldhy yqblh allah wydaefh lakum adeafana kthyrt"
  30,40,"allh wahdah hu aladhi khalaqakum -ayha alnas- thuma razaqakum fi hadhih alhyat, thuma yumitukum bantha' ajalkm, thuma yabeathukum min alqubur 'ahya' llhsab waljza', hal min shurakayikum man yafeal min dhlkm min shy'? tnzzah allah wtqddas ean shirk hwla' almushrikin bh"
  30,41,"zhr alfasad fi albari walbhr, kaljdb waqilat al'amtar wakathrat al'amrad walawbyt; wdhlk bsbb almeasy alty yqtrfha albshr; lysybhm beqwbt bed 'aemalahum alty emlwha fi aldnya; kay yatubuu 'iilaa allah -sbhanh- wyrjeu ean almeasy, ftslh ahwalhm, wtstqym amwrhm"